        "System.Description": "VCS Branch: zeus-1_0_2-1912<hr>As part to our Bankruptcy/Debtor in Possession Account Standardization Project, we are looking at the current ownership structures and relationships codes that are used by all affiliate banks when setting these accounts up through Zeus. With the support and guidance of our Legal Counsel, Kami Peterson, we have concluded that these accounts will be required to be opened using the following ownership structures and their associated relationship codes (attached)\n<br><br>This is a compliance mandated change. \n<br><br>See attached list of Ownership changes. <hr>Reporter: Mohammed Mohiuddin<hr>External ID: 1912<hr>Components: <hr>Affiliates affected: NBA,NSB,VBC,ZFNB,ABT,CBT<hr>Original assignee: Zeus Ready for Test<hr><div>Found with a Test Case</div><div><br></div><div>Additional Request from Amy Miller on this project:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\">&quot;Can we submit a JIRA\nticket for a small update in Zeus for VBC only? I need the \u201cnon-title\u201d client\nrelationship added to the account structure of \u201ctrust\u201d as this is the only\naffiliate it is missing from. &quot;</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>Per Trung, current code is:&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">For Vectra:</p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">Signer 0 (first signer)</p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Trust&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Beneficiary&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Trustee&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Co-Trustee&quot;</span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">Signer 1 (second signer)</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Trustee&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Co-Trustee&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Trust&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Non-Title&quot;</span>);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">Rest of signer</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Trustee&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Co-Trustee&quot;</span>);</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;text-autospace:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; pLB-&gt;AddString(<span style=\"color:#A31515;\">&quot;Non-Title&quot;</span>);</span></p><br></div><div>See attached email for additional details</div>",
